Film Session App Prebuild Plan

Product Scope (MVP first)





Lock the first release to one clear user promise: scan QR, login, take limited one-shot film-style photos, view/download for 30 days.



Keep controls intentionally minimal: fixed filter by host or small preset list (3-5 max), optional session password, no retakes.



Limit host complexity in v1: create session, configure rules, pay once, monitor submissions, end session.

Suggested Architecture (low risk, low ops)





Frontend: Next.js web app optimized for mobile camera flow (getUserMedia, playsinline, explicit tap-to-start camera).



Auth: Email magic link (or OTP) to reduce password friction after QR scan.



Backend: Postgres + server API routes (session creation, policy checks, upload signing, payment webhooks).



Storage: Start with S3-compatible bucket with lifecycle delete at 30 days; choose provider based on expected egress.



Payments: Stripe Checkout one-time payment per session with webhook-based activation.

